    "The studies on UNet and ResUNet models, which are also taken as a basis in the study, are presented below in general; Huang et al.",
    "have achieved vessel segmentation, which is difficult even for expert healthcare professionals, using the 3D-UNet structure they developed.",
    "For this, they used Sliver07 and 3Dircadb general datasets.",
    "In their study, they obtained average dice and sensitivity performance values of 75.3% and 76.7%, respectively [25].For white blood cell segmentation, Lu et al.",
    "developed a new deep learning algorithm (WBC-Net)."
